track_notes: Do not try this path! I messed up all the way raound!

Starting from the RN85, you must cross the river and start the ascent; do not follow the water on the left, but walk up instead, the path is easy until you must go on the left and start the climb in between trees and later some easy rocks.

This is the ultimate version!!!
You can park in the shadow of the trees and cross the small river (no water in summer) Then turn right. The walk is easy until you leave the forest road; go to the left, and try to follow a small path, to the ridge; you must use you hand to get the final crest. Plenty room on summit
